I generally stay away from liquid blush because of the lack of pigment, but @juviasplace has entered the Liquid Blush chat.

These new blushes are radiant, blendable, pigmented & buildable and they come in 12 shades. Perfect for all skin types and they are absolutely gorgeous and so pigmented!

Use my code “ohemaa” at checkout for an added discount and please be careful becuase it is easy to overdo it with these blushes. | Juvia’s Place Partner 

#BlushingWithJuvias #JPLiquidBlushed #JPSummerBlush #JuviasPlace #blush #blusher

These maybe the best liquid blushes in existence!

Listennn when I saw @nikescanvas try the purple blush, I ran to @juviasplace and bought it, now let me tell you why.

- the pigment, we all know Juvia’s place doesn’t put out a launch that is not inclusive and these blushes are no exception, dark skin makeup lovers can use more than 6 shades in a 12 shade range, not just one or two.

- Radiant finish means it can be used my all skin types, I have oily skin and the blendablity makes it possible to blend it over makeup, even powder without it getting patchy.

If you want to know more about these blushes and see a few swatches of them my full, detailed review is up on my Channel!
